      <arrangement id="aspace_6c0ec1e12e73802b39884be55e6c6f7b">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is divided into five series: 1. Articles and clippings, 2. Correspondence, 3. Biographical material by Gladys Adelina Lewis, 4. Photos, postcards and scrapbooks, and 5. Ephemera.</p>  
      </arrangement>
